### 更新任务配置{ #update-a-job-configuration } 

使用以下端点和JSON有效负载格式，通过参数更新作业：

    PUT /api/jobConfiguration/{id}

```json
{
  "name": "analytics last two years",
  "enabled": true,
  "cronExpression": "0 0 3 ? * MON",
  "jobType": "ANALYTICS_TABLE",
  "jobParameters": {
    "lastYears": "3",
    "skipTableTypes": [],
    "skipResourceTables": false
  }
}
```

